      "Synchronization\n",
      "-------------------------------------\n",
      "\n",
      "```\n",
      "   int MPI_Barrier(MPI_Comm comm)\n",
      "```\n",
      "\n",
      "Python (mpi4py)\n",
      "\n",
      "```\n",
      "   comm.Barrier(self)\n",
      "   comm.barrier(self)\n",
      "```"
